{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"a9420a91-06ba-40cf-aed6-a5dc38c09e9e","content":"I can help guide you through analyzing your crash dump. The `dump-collect` skill I have available is specifically for **collecting** dumps, not analyzing them — so let me give you direct guidance instead.\n\nHere are your main options for analyzing a `.dmp` file:\n\n### `dotnet-dump analyze` (cross-platform)\n```bash\n# Install the tool\ndotnet tool install -g dotnet-dump\n\n# Open the dump\ndotnet-dump analyze your-file.dmp\n```\nUseful commands inside the analyzer:\n- `clrstack` — managed call stack of the crashing thread\n- `pe` — print the last exception\n- `dumpheap -stat` — heap summary\n- `threads` — list all threads\n- `setthread <id>` + `clrstack` — inspect other threads\n\n### `lldb` (Linux/macOS)\n```bash\n# With SOS debugging extension\ndotnet-sos install\nlldb --core your-file.dmp\n# Then inside lldb:\nsos clrstack\nsos printexception\n```\n\n### Visual Studio (Windows)\n- **File → Open → File** → select the `.dmp`\n- Click **\"Debug with Managed Only\"**\n- VS will show the exception, call stack, and locals\n\n---\n\n**Recommended starting point:** Run `dotnet-dump analyze` and use `pe` (print exception) to see what exception caused the crash, then `clrstack` to see where it happened. Want me to walk you through any of these steps?","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"1d4f8828-becc-46f2-ab80-2235e60a8ded","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user is asking about analyzing a .dmp crash dump file. Let me check the available skills - there's a `dump-collect` skill, but its description specifically says:\n\n- USE FOR: enabling automatic crash dumps, capturing dumps, setting up dump collection\n- DO NOT USE FOR: analyzing or debugging dumps, post-mortem investigation with lldb/windbg/dotnet-dump analyze\n\nSo the dump-collect skill is NOT appropriate here. The user wants to analyze a dump, not collect one.\n\nLet me help them directly with guidance on analyzing crash dumps.","outputTokens":490,"requestId":"DA12:1F894F:58E540:657FBC:6A03DA18"},"id":"8e4b1840-cff6-4ab9-874e-4678b84f000f","timestamp":"2026-05-13T01:55:51.938Z","parentId":"7b30411a-5db7-4ed1-8e11-f6f2205b7ce2"}
